Yeah, "Details" is an unbelievable album. Even today, it still sounds excellent.

I really can't believe "Shh" nor "Flicks" were never singles from Details, they are two of the best songs on the album. Although the whole album is damn good. Those ones really stand out in my opinion. I'm sure others will agree.
Oh...I should mention...thanks for the up escapist!

You're welcome :) But although I can back you on Flicks, my faves are Only Got One and Hear Me Out. Still, picking out the tracks on that album that don't stand out is easier, just Psychobabble and Maddening Shroud. The rest are all amazing, IMO.
